text: Nataliya Shtaymets (born 5 November 1963) is a Kazakhstani cross-country skier. She competed in two events at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Kazakhstan Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
